{
  "title": "详解 Linux 下 SSH 远程文件传输命令 scp",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><br></div><div><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-align: center; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一、scp是什么?</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　scp是secure copy的简写，用于在Linux下进行远程拷贝文件的命令，和它类似的命令有cp，不过cp只是在本机进行拷贝不能跨服务器，而且scp传输是加密的。可能会稍微影响一下速度。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">二、scp有什么用?</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　1、我们需要获得远程服务器上的某个文件，远程服务器既没有配置ftp服务器，没有开启web服务器，也没有做共享，无法通过常规途径获得文件时，只需要通过scp命令便可轻松的达到目的。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2、我们需要将本机上的文件上传到远程服务器上，远程服务器没有开启ftp服务器或共享，无法通过常规途径上传是，只需要通过scp命令便可以轻松的达到目的。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">三、scp使用方法</span></strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、获取远程服务器上的文件</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">scp -P 2222 <a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a>:/root/lnmp0.4.tar.gz /home/lnmp0.4.tar.gz</p></blockquote><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上端口大写P 为参数，2222 表示更改SSH端口后的端口，如果没有更改SSH端口可以不用添加该参数。 <a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a> 表示使用root用户登录远程服务器<a href=\"http://www.vpser.net/\">www.vpser.net</a>，:/root/lnmp0.4.tar.gz 表示远程服务器上的文件，最后面的/home/lnmp0.4.tar.gz表示保存在本地上的路径和文件名。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、获取远程服务器上的目录</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">scp -P 2222 -r <a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a>:/root/lnmp0.4/ /home/lnmp0.4/</p></blockquote><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上端口大写P 为参数，2222 表示更改SSH端口后的端口，如果没有更改SSH端口可以不用添加该参数。-r 参数表示递归复制(即复制该目录下面的文件和目录);<a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a> 表示使用root用户登录远程服务器<a href=\"http://www.vpser.net/\">www.vpser.net</a>，:/root/lnmp0.4/ 表示远程服务器上的目录，最后面的/home/lnmp0.4/表示保存在本地上的路径。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、将本地文件上传到服务器上</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">scp -P 2222 /home/lnmp0.4.tar.gz <a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a>:/root/lnmp0.4.tar.gz<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></blockquote><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上端口大写P 为参数，2222 表示更改SSH端口后的端口，如果没有更改SSH端口可以不用添加该参数。 /home/lnmp0.4.tar.gz表示本地上准备上传文件的路径和文件名。<a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a> 表示使用root用户登录远程服务器<a href=\"http://www.vpser.net/\">www.vpser.net</a>，:/root/lnmp0.4.tar.gz 表示保存在远程服务器上目录和文件名。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、将本地目录上传到服务器上</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 10px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">scp -P 2222 -r /home/lnmp0.4/ <a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a>:/root/lnmp0.4/<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></blockquote><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上端口大写P 为参数，2222 表示更改SSH端口后的端口，如果没有更改SSH端口可以不用添加该参数。-r 参数表示递归复制(即复制该目录下面的文件和目录);/home/lnmp0.4/表示准备要上传的目录，<a href=\"mailto:root@www.vpser.net\">root@www.vpser.net</a> 表示使用root用户登录远程服务器<a href=\"http://www.vpser.net/\">www.vpser.net</a>，:/root/lnmp0.4/ 表示保存在远程服务器上的目录位置。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5、可能有用的几个参数 :</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">-v 和大多数 linux 命令中的 -v 意思一样 , 用来显示进度 . 可以用来查看连接 , 认证 , 或是配置错误 .</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">-C 使能压缩选项 .</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">-4 强行使用 IPV4 地址 .</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">-6 强行使用 IPV6 地址 .</p></li></ul></div>"
